com.darwinreforged.server.core.commands.context

Class AbstractCommandValue<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.darwinreforged.server.core.commands.context.AbstractCommandValue<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type parameter of the value stored
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CommandArgument, CommandFlag

    public abstract class AbstractCommandValue<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    The abstract command value object, holding a pair of key and value objects. This should only be generated by a CommandBus instance, and parsed by a CommandContext instance.
